    dc:creator "Fallon, Phillip J." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic review of tropical western Atlantic shallow water Drilliidae (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Conoidea) including descriptions of 100 new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263429> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263429>
    dc:description "PLATE 128. Lissodrillia simpsoni (Dall, 1887). Upper panel. Figs. 1 – 3: lectotype, Tampa Bay, Hillsborough Co. (USNM 61040). Fig. 1: ventral, lateral & dorsal views; Fig. 2: enlarged view of protoconch (not to scale); Fig. 3: apical view, V = varix, L = edge of outer lip. Lower panel. Specimens from different localities and habitats, all W Florida. Figs. 4 – 8: off Panama City, Bay Co. (DMNH 107133); Figs. 9 – 11: off Destin, Okaloosa Co. (UF 257198); Figs. 12 – 24: St. Joe Bay, Gulf Co. (shallow water; author’s coll.); and Figs. 25 – 30: W of Egmont Key, Hillsborough Co. (deep water; UF 470336)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263429/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

